    "description": "itsumo.inc. provides direct-to-consumer and e-commerce marketing services to brand manufacturers primarily in Japan. The company offers consulting, attracting customers, operation agency, logistics/backyard, strategy planning, site construction/operation, digital marketing, and fulfillment, as well as overseas sale services for e-commerce business. It also provides multi-channel development on brand EC sites; M&A and growth support for D2C and EC brands; EC human resource development; and SNS and EC promotion planning and operation. The company's customers include national manufacturers, small and medium-sized companies, and local governments; and various industries, such as cosmetics, food, home appliances, interior good, apparel, and babies products. itsumo.inc. was incorporated in 2007 and is headquartered in Chiyoda, Japan."
